Refactor navigation and pages, add Tentang Kami
Replaces 'Galeri' and 'Referensi' with 'Pengalaman' and 'Tentang Kami' in navigation and routes. Moves gallery and reference data to pengalaman, merges galeri and referensi pages into pengalaman, and adds a new Tentang Kami page with company info and map.
